<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>287</hymn_number>
<title>TO THE WORK</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Sem hitiu! sem hitiu! Pathien suokte I hiu,
 I Lalpau nungzuiin A sep bang sem hitiu;
 A thilhih theihna'n I hatnau hihthak zel ding,
 Sep ding i neih chenguh, theihtawp in sem hitiu.

[V2]
 Sem hitiu! Sem hitiu!
 Sem hitiu! Sem hitiu!
 Kinema ngak zingin,
 Lalpa hung masieh, sem hitiu.

[V3]
 2. Sem hitiu! sem hitiu! gilkielte an piei tiu,
 Hinna tuikhuk achun chaute chuh puih hiu hen!
 Kross leh a puonlap chuh I suonpen uh hi hen,
 &quot;Hukdamna manbei&quot; ti a I phuon lai u hin.

[V4]
 3. Sem hitiu! sem hitiu! sep ding I nei chiet ui,
 Thimna lalgam leh gitlohna chu tawm un au;
 Lalpa Jehovah min chuh chawihsan hung hintin,
 &quot;Hukdamna manbei&quot; ti'n chawihat la sak hina.

[V5]
 4. Sem hitiu! sem hitiu! Lalpa hatna mangin,
 Lalpuon leh lallukhuk kipahman in mui tiu;
 Mi ginumte In a chuh I chen tieng u leh,
 &quot;Hukdamna manbei&quot; ti'n tatte tawh la sai tiu.</lyrics>
</song>